#

Fruity Sushi Rolls

15 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

JapaneseFusion

Course:

SnackDessert

Tags:

EasyHealthySweetSnackDessert

Description

Refreshing and sweet sushi rolls filled with colorful fruits, perfect for a light snack or dessert!

Ingredients

  • sushi rice: 1 cup
  • rice vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • sugar: 1 tablespoon
  • nori sheets: 4 sheets
  • strawberries: 1 cup, sliced
  • kiwi: 1, sliced
  • mango: 1, sliced
  • banana: 1, sliced
  • honey: to drizzle (optional)
